<h1>Gunpla API Documentation</h1>

<p>This API lets you access and manage Gunpla products. Use the endpoints below to fetch or modify Gunpla data.</p>

<h2>Base URL</h2>
<p><code>https://localhost:7269/api/Gunpla</code></p>

<h2>Available Endpoints</h2>
<ul>
    <li><code>GET /api/Gunpla</code> - Get all Gunpla items</li>
    <li><code>GET /api/Gunpla/{id}</code> - Get a single Gunpla item</li>
    <li><code>POST /api/Gunpla</code> - Add a new Gunpla </li>
    <li><code>PUT /api/Gunpla/{id}</code> - Update a Gunpla item</li>
    <li><code>DELETE /api/Gunpla/{id}</code> - Delete a Gunpla item</li>
</ul>

